latestPosts.caption:
I still can’t believe it’s been over a year since I arrived in Melbourne , Australia 🇦🇺 as an international student. I came here with nothing but a trolley bag full of clothes and eyes full of dreams. This was the final presentation of the semester, and I’m just trying—and hoping—for the best, and for more opportunities to come my way.
I truly can’t believe I’ve done it all on my own. It was me who helped myself survive in Australia. And today, I’m so incredibly thankful to myself for that.
